&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/NYC-AVENUE-NIGHTCLUB-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8351&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/NYC-AVENUE-NIGHTCLUB-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;NYC- AVENUE NIGHTCLUB- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;65&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;Tucked between the Meatpacking District and Chelsea is Avenue, a two level lounge where a downtown vibe meets uptown sophistication. Relatively compact in size with a soaring vaulted ceiling and oak paneled walls, the ambiance is intimate where beautiful guests are able to dance and socialize. A small bites menu featuring comfort foods is featured along with creative cocktails and bottle service. Attire is dressy-chic.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Avenue via email only at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:dinersclubnyc@taogroup.com&quot;&gt;dinersclubnyc@taogroup.com&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention that the booking is for a reservation at AVENUE New York&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for up to 2 guests in total.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Upscale, trendy. No sneakers, hats, boots, athletic wear, or shorts for men. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late arrivals past midnight will be required to pay any required cover charges, despite having a reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife Access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

